OL,3,COfsted reform delays 'put more lives
OL,4,Cat risk', Ruth Perry's sister will warn
OL,6,FIn a speech to delegates at the
OL,7,Fconference in Bournemouth, the sister
OL,8,Fof Mrs Perry is expected to say: "I am
OL,9,Fworried that the people who could
OL,10,Fbring about real change might only be
OL,11,Fpaying lip service to the lessons we
OL,12,Fmust learn.
OL,14,F"I hope we do learn, and learn
OL,15,Fquickly. The Ofsted system of
OL,16,Finspections is fatally flawed. It
OL,17,Fdoesn't serve parents, or pupils, or
OL,18,Fteachers. It must change."
