OL,4,Cat risk', Ruth Perry's sister will warn
OL,6,F"There seems to be a lot of
OL,7,Funnecessary delay."
OL,9,FShe will add: "How many more teachers
OL,10,Fwill suffer from an inherently flawed,
OL,11,Fbadly run inspection process in the
OL,12,Fmeantime?
OL,14,F"How many more children will lose
OL,15,Fanother dedicated headteacher to a
OL,16,Fforced resignation, a nervous
OL,17,Fbreakdown or worse?
OL,19,F"Delays and obfuscation put more lives
OL,20,Fat risk. It's not acceptable to play
OL,21,Fpolitics with people's wellbeing."
