OL,3,COfsted reform delays 'put more lives
OL,4,Cat risk', Ruth Perry's sister will warn
OL,6,F"But teaching unions have been calling
OL,7,Ffor the abolition of Ofsted for 30
OL,8,Fyears. And what good has that done
OL,9,Fteachers? Look at the evidence. How
OL,10,Fdid calling for Ofsted to be abolished
OL,11,Fhelp Ruth?
OL,13,F"No-one is going to abolish Ofsted any
OL,14,Ftime soon, whether the Education
OL,15,FSecretary is part of a Conservative or
OL,16,Fa Labour government."
OL,18,FAt the start of the year, Ofsted
OL,19,Finspections were paused in England to
OL,20,Fensure inspectors were given mental
OL,21,Fhealth awareness training.
